data.description: This 3 bed 1 bath charming 1.5 story home has tons of potential! New roof and siding in 2021, updated windows, maintenance free walk in shower, attractive updated kitchen with an abundance of natural lighting. The large finished lower level has an office and cozy family room with bar and wood burning stove. Check out the large fenced in back yard! Great location with all your shopping needs within walking distance.... must see!
